SaveThread - Class in Threads
SaveThread is an implementation of Runnable that retrieves images from a queue generated by a GrayscaleThread and saves them to a local folder.

SingleThreaded - Class in Threads
SingleThreaded is a class designed to perform a single-threaded version of image downloading, converting to grayscale, and saving to a local folder on the user's computer.
